data.description: Privacy and serenity abound on this very private 19+ acre estate. Enjoy the sounds of nature and watch the plentiful wildlife as you rock on the front porch or as you drive the many trails carved through the property. The home was custom built and offers the trending open great room, split floor plan, and volume ceilings. Thoughtful details include custom wood cabinets with a matching built-in china cabinet and display cases. The owner's suite offers an attached office/flex room, tiled shower, whirlpool tub and oversized walk-in closet. The outside amenities include an in-ground pool with screen enclosure, two car garage converted into an extra space that is perfect for entertaining. Added bonus features are the pole bar for covered storage, feed shed, pond, separate septic and electric for an RV hook-up, whole house generator and Starlink Internet!
